{
  "stem": "9777.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were standing, and they just shot two people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "One man was getting ready to expire.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "No medical help whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They didn't give him any medical help.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The woman died right away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She was lucky.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The man got some kind of a blood poisoning, I presume, account of he was around all those weeks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was laying in one of the smaller storage rooms indoors.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And before we left from there, he was, like, saying his good-byes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Showed the picture of his wife, if he ever-- we survive, we should go and say hello to his wife.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But he was a young married man, and he had small children, something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But nobody really kept any kind of mementos like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "No, they were very cruel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We worked there in the kitchen after a while, since the ground work didn't work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And since we worked in the kitchen, we were mostly indoors peeling potatoes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This was the kitchen work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I presume you would call it-- you had to have a norm how much potatoes you peeled.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You just couldn't peel a little bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You had to peel a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And one day, they decided there was too many of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So they made an appell, an appeal like.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They stood us up on the yard and selected the people who had any kind of a complaints.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So one of my girlfriends was complaining that her feet is swollen and that she can't put on her shoes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I wore her shoe, and she had gotten a man's shoe, account of all of us had, like, frozen soles, not being able to get undressed never, account of the cold.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So we were with our shoes on constantly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "With our coats and with our clothes, we were wearing it for weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
